T*
(1. Read the question or example and identify the part connected to Computer Basics.) Tj
T*
(2. Recall the specific rule, process, or principle behind hardware, software, input,) Tj
T*
(processing, storage, and output.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct logical procedure step by step instead of jumping to the answer.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the result carefully and confirm that it matches the requirement of the topic.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
