T*
(Worked Example 1) Tj
T*
(1. Start with an example based on tracing how data enters, is processed, and is) Tj
T*
(displayed.) Tj
T*
(2. Identify the exact idea in hardware, software, input, processing, storage, and output) Tj
T*
(that the question is testing.) Tj
T*
(3. Apply the correct method for Computer Basics step by step without skipping reasoning.) Tj
T*
(4. Check the final answer and explain why it is correct.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Worked Example 2) Tj
T*
(1. Choose a second example that still focuses on identifying system components and their) Tj
